---
By: A Spiritual Warrior
Locus:
  Page: 490
  Verse: 6
Tags:
  - Wisdom
---
The wisest man simply has nothing to say. He realizes that all thoughts,
words and acts and even enlightenment are only relative. ...The very wisest
spiritual soul knows for a fact that he is ignorant and understands
nothing, for his knowledge is relative unto a higher reality.
